and you're gonna run away?

01:25:28.891 --> 01:25:33.193
You came here,
told us how we should be.

01:25:33.896 --> 01:25:36.363
No matter what,
keep on trying,

01:25:36.365 --> 01:25:38.365
keep hoping for better things!

01:25:38.367 --> 01:25:40.834
